HedgeBoard is the “MyFxBook” of Crypto. It’s a Trading Performance Verification Tracking System. Using blockchain technology it’s able to record, store & secure all trading data of a traders portfolio & rate there performance using our complex algorithms to give the most accurate profile rating. This will verify all the self proclaimed Crypto Guru’s out there with our leader board. Every trade is recorded on the blockchain using smart contracts in real time. So no trader can go back & alter there records to look better. This is the only way to verify real traders & pay according to what there trades are really worth. Never pay for a losing trade again‼️ HedgeBoard incorporated a staking method to insure all costumers are guaranteed there purchase fee if the trade signal is a fail + commission.

node.text:
The jaw dropping @jacobanco Billionaire III. The 18k white gold case and bracelet are paved with approximately 580 carats of invisibly set diamonds arranged in a rarely seen horizontal pattern.

First introduced in 2015, the Billionaire unique piece adorned with Emerald-Cut Diamonds turned heads with its approximate carat weight of 260 carats (its price tag surpassing $18 million). 

Now, the collection adds another limited-edition Billionaire diamond-encrusted tourbillon timepiece, The Billionaire III.

@jacobandco combine their phenomenal watch making skills and true luxury with the Billionaire III.
